        <section class="foam-eurasia-section">
            <div class="foam-eurasia-container">
                <div class="foam-eurasia-text">
                    <h2>Rise in Load Engineering: LES-EXPO</h2>
                    <p> <strong>LES-EXPO</strong>, the region's most comprehensive fair for construction equipment and
                        heavy vehicle
                        solutions, brings together the industry to showcase the latest technology in the freight
                        engineering sector.
                    </p>

                    <p>Today, efficiency, safety and sustainability are indispensable concepts in the <strong>
                            construction,
                            mining, logistics and energy sectors.</strong> The companies that are pioneers of this
                        transformation are
                        making a difference in production with cranes with increased load-carrying capacities, smart
                        excavators and automation-supported heavy-duty vehicles.
                    </p>

                    <p>The latest products and technologies exhibited at the fair are a source of inspiration not only
                        for industry professionals, but also for all investors who want to shape the engineering
                        solutions of the future. The graphic on the right is a concrete indicator of this rapid
                        development process. R&D investments, sustainable designs and digitalization are increasing the
                        growth momentum of the sector every day.</p>

                    <p>LES-EXPO is not just an exhibition; it is a strategic platform that takes the pulse of the sector
                        and opens doors to business connections. The freight engineering technologies of the future are
                        shaped here.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="foam-eurasia-image">
                    <img src="./images/grafik.png" alt="Foam Eurasia Grafik">
